<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.4.3">
<l>curikaiyun teṟivilluñ ceṇṭu kōlum</l>
<l rend="indent">mēlāṭai yuntōḻaṉ mārkoṇ ṭōṭa</l>
<l>vorukaiyā loruvaṉtaṉ tōḷai yūṉṟi</l>
<l rend="indent">yānirai yiṉamīḷak kuṟitta caṅkam</l>
<l>varukaiyil vāṭiya piḷḷai kaṇṇaṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">mañcaḷum mēṉiyum vaṭivuṅ kaṇṭāḷ</l>
<l>arukē niṉṟāḷeṉ peṇōkkik kaṇṭā</l>
<l rend="indent">ḷatukaṇ ṭivvūroṉ ṟupuṇark kiṉṟatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As [his] friends run with [his] knife, small bow, bat, and shawl,</l>
<l>With one hand resting on the shoulder of another [boy],</l>
<l rend="indent">[and with the other holding] the conch</l>
<l rend="indent">that he blows to call back the cow herd,</l>
<l>she sees the turmeric colour, body, and beauty of [my] boy Kaṇṇaṉ,</l>
<l rend="indent">who weakens upon return.</l>
<l>My girl stood right next to [him] and stared.</l>
<l rend="indent"> Seeing that, something will surely be said in this village.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
